English

This Archive contains two different Directories :

1) DC-Levels

Here you can find some new Levels for the Game "WORMS THE DIRECTORS CUT"

Just copy them to "TWCUSTOM" und they can be played. Except the Level
"Rainforest" all Levels are "Dual-Layers", that means they have an
extra-background.

For that reason and because they all use 16 colors, this Levels can ONLY be
used with "WORMS THE DIRECTORS CUT" !

2) DC-Grafik

Here you can find two graphics for each level. One for the "play-level"
and one for the background. With "WORMS THE DIRECTORS CUT" you also got a
tool (WORMSPREFS), that combines these two graphics to one "Dual-Layer-Level".

So you can see, how easy it is to create simple Dual-Layers. And because
not all colors are used yet, you are free to add some graphic-objects by
yourself (with DPAINT or any similar drawing-programm).

If you want, you can also create new Levles, which are very complex (the
rooms of a house, that you will see, if the walls are "destroyed"). But for
that you will need a lot of time and patient ...

(C)-Info : All levels are NOT drawn by myself ! I got them from different
PD-sources (Aminet). They have all been created for the first part of WORMS.
I only converted and enhanced them for "WORMS THE DIRECTORS CUT".

